snippet.title: Movies Coming Out In 2022 That We Can't Wait For
snippet.description:
After a somewhat muted 2021 when it come to theatrical releases, 2022 looks like the year of cinema. From long-awaited sequels like James Cameron's "Avatar 2" to brand new films from beloved auteurs like Park Chan-wook's "Decision to Leave," it seems like there's going to be a film for everyone in the coming year. Even Pixar is returning to the "Toy Story" universe for a fifth go-around... in a way. If you've had trouble keeping up with what new releases you'll need to pre-order your tickets for, we've got you covered. Here are the most anticipated movies of 2022.
